==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bolero
<hw>Bo*le"ro</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp.]</ety>
<fld>(Mus.)</fld> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A Spanish dance, or the lively music
which accompanies it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A kind of small outer jacket, with or without
sleeves, worn by women.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>bolete</ent>⟦br⟧
